    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Adult female Eriococcus paranaensis Foldi & Kozár sp. nov. Where A = dorsal macrotubular ducts of two sizes; B = dorsal microtubular duct; C = spinose setae; D = 5-locular pore; E = metathoracic claw; F = metathoracic coxa with translucent pores; G = cruciform pore; H = short ventral seta; I = antenna." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5096727/files/figure.png" ;
